text.tspan: Prevalence of bipolar disorder in males vs. females, 2019
Share of the male population versus female population suffering from bipolar disorder. Figures attempt to provide a true estimate (going
beyond reported diagnosis) of bipolar disorder prevalence based on medical, epidemiological data, surveys and meta-regression modelling.
Data source: IHME, Global Burden of Disease (2019)
